    # "About half an hour later, Whitney picks me up at my house and we drive over to Jackson Burger, chit-chatting along the way."
    "Unos treinta minutos más tarde, Whitney me recoge en mi casa y nos dirigimos a Jackson Burger, charlando por el camino."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyjacksonburgerdate.rpy:30
translate spanish whitneyjacksonburgerstartdate_e86c27fb:

    # "Then we sit in the back in my usual booth."
    "Luego nos sentamos en la parte de atrás, en mi mesa habitual."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyjacksonburgerdate.rpy:34
translate spanish whitneyjacksonburgerstartdate_c38e7520:

    # "We sit and chat more while eating our burgers."
    "Nos sentamos y seguimos charlando mientras comemos nuestras hamburguesas."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyjacksonburgerdate.rpy:37
translate spanish whitneyjacksonburgerstartdate_a5a3cfb1:

    # "When we're finished, she pays for the food and I cover the tip, then we go outside."
    "Cuando terminamos, ella paga la comida y yo pongo la propina, y luego salimos."

